Yeah Today i was sick. Ddidn't go to school, just slept allday. Wednesday was crazy! i went to the powderpuff game and i heard talk about a hudge fight. So i followed the crowed for about an hour and finally a fight broke out. At first it was against 2 people not to say any names. Later the fight got worse and everyone started getting into it. It was crazy! parents were tring to brake it up but it was much to big to do so. Finally the cops came and everyone ran away! IT was crazy!!!

Yeah so,
Last night was crazy! Juniors vs. seniors was kickn off. Derek, Dez, Kara, Jena, Kyle and me all went out T.Ping last night and hit a few seniors. we stopped at meijer and talked to all the drunk people from the party. most of them were alright but a few were pretty trashed. After meijer we got pulled over by a cop and it almost made derek piss his pants. I thought it was great but everyone else thought it was scary. I always like it when i almost get busted it just sends a rush through me. Anyways thats it! cant wait for the weekend!

Anyways my numer is 730-0040 and if you get the voice mail its my dad not me so just ignore it. Later PEace!!!!

Today was tight! school was so boring until theater tech hit then it was fun. Recently i've been tring to take advantage of the warm weather thats left so i decided to go to the beach and go skimboarding. After school i called around to find  someone to skim with but everyone was going to the girls basketball game, so that didn't work out. But then my wonderful girlfriend called me and said she would go. which was defiantly fine with me because come on wouldn't any guy rather go to the beach with a hott chick anyday, than go to the beach with his friends! But i had a great time like always!
